舞台碌過去，壓死好多人<br />\n跟住我就嚇醒咗<br />\n<br />\n醒之後仲好記得幾百人嘅慘叫聲"},{"pid":"ab955a7bb9b0fb69d8ac881448987dc9736ecd2d","tid":1156431,"uid":120892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:17:39.000Z","msg":"另一次發夢響屋內湊朋友5歲大嘅女<br />\n睇住佢週屋走，又睇到電視話颶風逼近<br />\n跟住聽到個小朋友慘叫<br />\n跑入房，d窗原來未關好俾風扯走咗<br />\n風同雨係咁兜口面打埋黎<br />\n我想拉個小朋友離開間房<br />\n但一拖佢隻手發現好似冰咁凍<br />\n轉頭一望佢，已經成個人藍曬，死咗<br />\n嚇到我扎醒咗"},{"pid":"b8ec86556c668e76dc3cb83e415aceec1119cc4b","tid":1156431,"uid":78565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:19:06.000Z","msg":"發夢同龍心拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd229a651e94bbbf67d236228e205c818027f75e","tid":1156431,"uid":234737,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:37:25.000Z","msg":"去海邊釣魚 釣左幾個黑人上嚟 跟著同佢地踢波 踢完場波放返佢地落海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15f7800056d345726a96f83d128d5a8dac2d18e0","tid":1156431,"uid":160907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45a57cc2f53d7c8f1458c69bab76b048fea3fb63","tid":1156431,"uid":237568,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:39:43.000Z","msg":"試過發過三層夢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:52:25.000Z","msg":"試過死三次 每次以為冇事又要死"},{"pid":"b6666c0c1d01eee859fc9ac7ef86b4e63dc11d72","tid":1156431,"uid":25512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"192ec1ac82233274fd3fa6545455dedc30056752","tid":1156431,"uid":33441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54247fca5e9a138f039ef5a8e4ba1eeac27332cd","tid":1156431,"uid":108756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T03:00:31.000Z","msg":"睇黎樓主你平時成日諗埋啲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"